reviewText: Volume 4 has the same episodes as in Volume 2!

Who you gonna call? Of course this deserves 5 stars the cartoon series is great! It is so cool to show my children one of my favorite cartoons from my childhood. Bright and great sound, it is perfect to add to my movie collection

This is just a random selection of episodes from the first few seasons. It will not help if you are trying to get/complete the whole series. They are pretty good episodes, but not the best. And only 11 episodes.
